data.description: This is a MUST SEE custom built home. The attention to detail and quality of this home was not missed. Starting with the Safety and Energy saving technology. You must see it to appreciate it. As you enter the home you will be greeted by the stainless steel and bamboo foyer staircase that has step lights that activate at night. moving to the kitchen you will find an extra large island, gloss polyester cabinets, glass tile backsplash, and quartz counter tops. Also includes Energy Saving, on demand hot water in seconds from any faucet in this home. The Kitchen Aid stainless steel appliances stay. Entertain family dinners from the L-shaped booth for comfortable seating. The flooring consist of Calibamboo in the common areas, carpet in the family room and bedrooms, and tile in all bathrooms. This home also features radiant floor heating throughout the home and garage, including the basement. The living room has 7.1 surround sound and Philips Hue Accent lighting throughout. The Master includes a spa-like his and hers shower room, jacuzzi, mood lighting and a LARGE walk in closet that you will fall in love with. Call to see this home today!
